item.title: Help!@
item.dc:creator: @vManlyMan vManlyMan
item.description:
@vManlyMan wrote:

To add a portal go into client.java and search for

Then add

Where #### is your X coordinate, **** is your Y coordinate, and %%%% is your object ID.
The ID for a portal is 4150.

Then to make it tele you somewhere when you click on it go back into client.java and search

Under that add

if(objectID == %%%%) { toX = ####; toY = ****; heightLevel = @; }

Where %%%% is the same object ID that you used before. #### is your X coordinate that the tele will take you to, **** is your Y coordinate that the tele will take you to, and @ is the height that the tele will take you to. To add KQ just add it into autospawn.cfg
